What is Bitcoin Lightning?
--follow Andreas Antonopoulous for frequent and simply digestible videos on bitcoin/crypto topics--
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Z7Q0AwbKZX8
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rrr_zPmEiME&t
